text: Ellie Kemper (born May 2, 1980) is an American actress. She played Ms. Griggs in 21 Jump Street. She played Kelly Erin Hannon in The Office. Kemper was born in Kansas City, Missouri. ==References== Category:Actors from Kansas City, Missouri Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:1980 births Category:Living people
